	pets let their hair down (or strings loose) in No Strings Attached —a hila
	rious\, adults improv puppet show. After a long day entertaining the kids\
	, these puppets are ready to play—singing bawdy songs\, cracking jokes\, a
	nd getting up to all kinds of outrageous fun. And the best part? You call 
	the shots with your suggestions! Don’t miss this one-of-a-kind comedy show
	 at Pike Place Market. It’s puppets\, it’s improv\, and it’s guaranteed to
	 make you laugh. THIS SHOW CONTAINS MATURE CONTENT\, LANGUAGE\, AND SITUAT
